{"tid":1683075,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"小米手錶 11．5 發布 外觀激似 Apple Watch？","createTime":"2019-10-30T12:48:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T02:32:11.000Z","uid":58335,"like":4,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"791297b159fca21c59ebe279494bece36e018b2e","tid":1683075,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T12:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2485000/2486113/20191030_xiaomiwatch_01_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2485000%2F2486113%2F20191030_xiaomiwatch_01_1024.jpg&h=ea232cfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早前小米 Xiaomi 表明將於 11 月 5 日舉行新產品發布會，推出小米 CC9 Pro 手機、小米手錶以及小米電視 5 等產品，而在最近，小米創辦人雷軍直接把小米手錶真身 po 到微博！且慢！何解小米手錶外觀是如此的似曾相識呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2485000/2486113/20191030_xiaomiwatch_02_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2485000%2F2486113%2F20191030_xiaomiwatch_02_600.jpg&h=ad09d05c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小米 Xiaomi 將於 11 月 5 日舉行新產品發布會<br />\n發布會上會公布小米 CC9 Pro 手機、小米手錶以及小米電視 5 等產品<br />\n小米創辦人雷軍在微博直接將小米手錶真身曝光，不過當中外觀激似 Apple Watch<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2485000/2486113/20191030_xiaomiwatch_03_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2485000%2F2486113%2F20191030_xiaomiwatch_03_600.jpg&h=36ac9c33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n單看小米手錶的外觀，相信不少人已覺得跟 Apple Watch 有 9 成相似，畢竟小米手錶同樣是四方錶殼，而且右方一樣有數碼錶冠及 Home 按鍵，用來操控這款智能手錶的不同功能。規格方面，已知小米手錶會起用 Snapdragon Wear 3100 處理器、ARM Cortex A7 架構，並標榜數天的使用時間，以及內置獨立 Wi-Fi、藍牙、GPD、CPU、及 eSIM 等功能。此外，小米手錶也有一項頗為「估你唔到」的元素，就是在小米生態鏈部總經理屈恒的微博影片可見之短片播放功能。雖然當中強調為測試功能，但估計能跟用家見面的機會不低。只是，有多少人會願意在細小屏幕上觀賞短片？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2486113/%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%E6%89%8B%E9%8C%B6%2011%EF%BC%8E5%20%E7%99%BC%E5%B8%83%20%20%E5%A4%96%E8%A7%80%E6%BF%80%E4%BC%BC%20Apple%20Watch%EF%BC%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2486113%2F%25E5%25B0%258F%25E7%25B1%25B3%25E6%2589%258B%25E9%258C%25B6%252011%25EF%25BC%258E5%2520%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B8%2583%2520%2520%25E5%25A4%2596%25E8%25A7%2580%25E6%25BF%2580%25E4%25BC%25BC%2520Apple%2520Watch%25EF%25BC%259F&d=VY3E9QkOBFFWjsPhNJvPHvsf6ZhrNwlVLGl95Ukzwcs%3D&h=d97ee66c\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2486113/%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%E6%89%8B%E9%8C%B6%2011%EF%BC%8E5%20%E7%99%BC%E5%B8%83%20%20%E5%A4%96%E8%A7%80%E6%BF%80%E4%BC%BC%20Apple%20Watch%EF%BC%9F</a>"},{"pid":"83eedfecb4410b8bfef9269ae2099b5990c904f8","tid":1683075,"uid":4142,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T12:49:11.000Z","msg":"十成啦吓嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecec52ade72a9ee30ae05b396c0a0c4e2ab99a60","tid":1683075,"uid":26327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T12:49:19.000Z","msg":"點解要咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20730ee9ba81d78a82cd3a00ab38029ebd9cbcf2","tid":1683075,"uid":19566,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T12:49:36.000Z","msg":"抄抄抄淨係識抄<br />\n支那嘢講撚到自己有幾巴閉到頭來咪又係抄"},{"pid":"94f73357d9381f7c15ed0f82c08b2c09ff99420e","tid":1683075,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecec52ade72a9ee30ae05b396c0a0c4e2ab99a60","tid":1683075,"uid":26327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T12:49:19.000Z","msg":"點解要咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:30:25.000Z","msg":"你第一日識支那野咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d